asset.hookText: Werks Traveler 5.0 has been strategically engineered to weigh less, contain greater capacity and provide more packing options as a result of the intelligent Pack More System.  Inspired by the ingenuity and multi-functionality of the Original Swiss Army Knife, the Pack More System includes five different packing solutions.  Pack it your way and travel with more of the things that are important to you. 60 Second Version
